  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The Strategy is to create a China Aurix convergence platform, where platform components for SCC side will be implemented."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "This will make project life easy, since we have always a PF Base to start with."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The plan is to reuse component from below two platforms"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "Cerberus Platform - Where modules related to Aurix chip is available",
        "Hydra Platform - Reusable chip independent modules like LCM components are available"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Both are above platform deliveries shall be present in common Convergence base platform owned by a team called CART"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Our China Convergence Platform includes CART (Cerberus + Hydra) modules and few modules explicitly implemented for China convergence project requirements"
    },
